Type: Package
Package: adlgraphs
Title: Create Graphs with ADL Style and Branding
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jacob", "Dennen", , "jdennen@adl.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package is designed to make it easier for folks at CAR
    at ADL to make graphs. The package contains all of the different
    themes related to various graph styles, a guide to which colors to use
    and when, and various functions created related to various graphs
    (mainly for coefficient plots).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/JDenn0514/adlgraphs,
    https://jdenn0514.github.io/adlgraphs/
BugReports: https://github.com/JDenn0514/adlgraphs/issues
